(13820, 'Aloxi 0.25mg/5ml vial for i.v.', 'الوكسي 0.25 مجم/5مل فيال', '771', '1,101', 'Palonosetron', 'Mundipharma > multipharma', 'Vial', 'فيال', '', 'Antiemetic', '0.25mg', 'For the prevention of acute and delayed nausea and vomiting associated with initial and repeat courses of moderately emetogenic cancer chemotherapy, as well as prevention of acute nausea and vomiting associated with highly emetogenic cancer chemotherapy. Also used for the prevention of postoperative nausea and vomiting for up to 24 hours post operation.', '', '', 1372, '2025-03-20', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
